Class::XML::Parser

DESCRIPTION

Parses an XML file into a user-defined class hierarchy, with
optional DTD validation.

PREREQUISITES

XML::Parser - class used internally for parsing
Carp

OPTIONAL MODULES

XML::Checker::Parser - needed if DTD validation of the source XML is
  desired

BUILDING/INSTALLING

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

